Name: pyndexter
Version: 0.1
Summary: A full-text indexing abstraction layer for Python
Home-page: http://swapoff.org/pyndexter
Author: Alec Thomas
Author-email: alec@swapoff.org
License: BSD
Download-URL: http://swapoff.org/pyndexter
Description: Pyndexter (pronounced 'poindexter') is an abstraction layer for full-text indexing engines. In addition to adapters for Hyperestraier and Xapian, Pyndexter includes a native Python indexer.
